2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new quantization scheme for neural networks, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new method for optimizing neural network quantization, which is a subfield of AI. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper deals with neural networks and proposes a new method for quantization, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new quantization scheme that involves a reparameterization of the clipping function and weight normalization, which can be seen as algorithmic techniques.
